      "message": "As far as I know, we don\u0027t actually support any markdown syntax in `ann.Text`. They are meant to be treated as plain text (to be confirmed by nodir@chromium.org). Previously, those charathers are manually escaped because we are treating them as markdown in the frontend. Now we don\u0027t need to, because div blocks inside markdown will not be parsed as markdown anyway.",
